Ghetto Organized is the only album released by rap group, Gambino Family. It was released on October 20, 1998 through No Limit Records and was entirely produced by Beats By the Pound. The album made it high on the Billboard charts, making it to #15 on the Billboard 200 and #3 on the Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums, but the group never released a follow-up and have not been heard of since. The single "Studio B" was a minor success. There was also a promotional video for the song" Childhood Years".
